**Content approach:** Most competitors run a simple listicle — "X trends to try" — with 1 hero image per trend and minimal editorial depth. Very few include verified data (Fresha stats, Google Trends %). Almost none structure around a true "what's in vs. what's out" editorial frame backed by expert quotes and booking data.

